NBA ALL-STAR WEEKEND
February 18, 2011
Derrick Favors
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT
 
 
  
 
  
  
   


   DERRICK FAVORS: I worked hard and got better every game.  
  
  Q. What does it feel like to actually be selected --  
 DERRICK FAVORS: It's a great moment. It just shows hard work paying off. It's a great honor to be here.   
  
  Q. As far as the first half of the season, what's it been like working with Coach Avery? The little general as they say and stuff like that. What's that been like?  
 DERRICK FAVORS: Oh, it's been wonderful. Avery is a great coach and great motivator. He worked with me since training camp and I love playing for him. He's a great coach.   
   
